<div class="container" style="max-width:1400px">
  <h1 class="mt-5 mb-5 pt-5 text-center">Meet the Team</h1>
  <div class="profile-container w-100 d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between">
    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Piotr.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of Ouicity team member Piotr" %>
      <h3 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/PiotrekCodes" target="_blank"
                          class="logo-font fs-2 text-decoration-none">Piotr</a></h3>
      <h5 class="text-start">Head of Transportation 🚌</h5>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Piotr is charged with getting people, objects and information from point A to
      point B, whether that is using a 🚴🏻, 🚗 or an Action Cable channel. And they always cross the finish line!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Dari.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of Ouicity team member Dari" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/DariBerrie" target="_blank"
                          class="logo-font fs-2 text-decoration-none">Dari</a></h2>
      <h5 class="text-start">Head of Littering ♻️</h5>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">With a neurotic eye, Dari finds the forgotten trash, furniture, or extra divs in the
      streets and finds their true home: the 🗑 or as a new product for her side gig on
      <a href="http://www.valuejunk.site/" target="_blank">ValueJunk</a> ♻️.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Zsuzsanna.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of Ouicity team member Zsuzsanna" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/zynolia" target="_blank"
                          class="logo-font fs-2 text-decoration-none">Zsuzsanna</a></h2>
      <h5 class="text-start">Head of New Ideas 💡</h5>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Zsuzsanna is our city innovator expertly putting new ideas, suggestions, and intakes
      into action on the field! If you like it, Zsuzsanna is probably the 🧠 behind it!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Amanda.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of Ouicity team member Amanda" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/AmandaPerino" target="_blank"
                          class="logo-font fs-2 text-decoration-none">Amanda</a></h2>
      <h5 class="text-start">Head of Infrastructure 🛠</h5>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Amanda ensures the strong foundation and progress of Ouicity! From the ground up to our
      tallest 🗼, this planning maestro orchestrates the user journey from the first note to the finale!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
